            "date_published": "2023-04-13T04:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>This is a non-exhaustive roster of past and present membership and those affiliated with W2SZ. </p>\n<h2 id=\"Updates\"><a href=\"#Updates\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Updates\"></a>Updates</h2><p>We rely crowd-sourcing to make information accurate and updated. Contact us if you have clues.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>To nominate someone who’s missing from the list, email a club officer about the nominee.</li>\n<li>To nominate yourself, reach two listed hams who may know you, and ask them to recommend you.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"The-Grand-Roster\"><a href=\"#The-Grand-Roster\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"The Grand Roster\"></a>The Grand Roster</h2>",
